      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm just wondering why certain schools feel it's so urgent to do this right now? it feels like it's being pushed on families pretty aggressively. is there a specific reason why the educators think this is actually necessary for the kids rather than just being a distraction from regular subjects?",
